    "abstract": [
        {
            "text": "J o u r n a l P r e -p r o o f Journal Pre-proof J o u r n a l P r e -p r o o f Journal Pre-proof J o u r n a l P r e -p r o o f Journal Pre-proof -Shorter ventilation times table J o u r n a l P r e -p r o o f Journal Pre-proof",
